dcterms:description: ChFinAnn dataset consists of 32,040 financial documents, with 25,632 in the train set, 3,204 in the development set, and 3,204 in the test set. It includes five event types and contains 71% of single-event documents and 29% of multi-event documents.
dcterms:title: ChFinAnn

dcterms:description: DuEE-Fin dataset contains around 11,900 financial documents and includes 13 event types. The dataset does not contain the ground truth annotations for the test set, and the original development set is used as the test set.
